defaultThe Chairman:default A final question from me. Is it appropriate for the European Union to have a role in youth unemployment, and if so, why? Perhaps I may make a suggestion at this point. In our own country, we are not supposed to look at any trends that may be reflected in our statistics for three months. However, at the moment we are seeing a fall in youth unemployment in the 
