defaultMy last remark is that there is a slight contradiction here. I can appreciate that in some member states there will be a feeling that the EU should not do anything about the situation, but if the EU does not say or do anything, that could really endanger its whole purpose.
defaultYou mentioned that things are perhaps looking better in the 
defaultUK
